  </colgroup>
  <thead><tr><th>Value<th>Meaning</tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>TaxReportAndCertificate</code><td class="long">The custodian is to perform a reporting of type 11. For domestic taxpayers, a tax certificate shall be issued.</tr>
    <tr><td><code>Reclaim</code><td class="long">The custodian should create or forward the application for reclaim of withholding tax. Additional information for the application needs to be delivered.</tr>
    <tr><td><code>Relief</code><td class="long">The custodian provided relief at source and additional information gets provided via the request.</tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

