    <tr><td><code>Cash</code><td class="long">Payment in Cash.</tr>
    <tr><td><code>Shares</code><td class="long">Payment in Shares (stock dividend).</tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3 id="enum-receiptsanddeliveriesmode">ReceiptsAndDeliveriesMode</h3>

<p><em>Used in:</em> <code>2 Security Related Information.ReceiptsAndDeliveriesMode</code></p>

